<h2 class="text-center">Featured!</h2>

<div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
    <img src="~/img/Kitty.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Cat wearing cat sweater">
    <div class="card-body bg-light">
        <h5 class="card-title text-dark">Kitty Sweater</h5>
        <p class="card-text text-dark">Red kitty sweater with white designs to help keep your kitty warm during winter!</p>
